title: A muted, dusky pile of abstract houses and offices, expressionistic twisting flying roads and chunky cubist auto parts. They bend and flow into each other as if they were a dreamlike fluid. From the.flowing pile grow three big, vivid, natural trees.Climbing the pile, as if they were bouldering or surfing, are four giant, lanky, yellow, androgynous humanoids -- two male and two female. The style of the urban fluid chaos pile is cubist, expressionistic, surreal, warped -- but the trees and the giant humanoids are realistic.
pid: ab1a8dbd-55f6-4b39-a4be-83ae39154748
